							<img class="size-full wp-image-2356000" src="http://images.indianexpress.com/2015/04/nepal-victim-l.jpg" alt="Water bottles are used to apply traction to the fractured legs of a girl, in Kathmandu Wednesday.  (Source: Reuters photo)" width="759" height="422" /> Water bottles are used to apply traction to the fractured legs of a girl, in Kathmandu Wednesday. (Source: Reuters photo)						</div>
